sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant ESP as ESP32 (Host)
    participant W5500 as W5500 (Slave)

    Note over ESP, W5500: 1. Network Information Initialization (Common Registers)
    
    ESP->>W5500: Software Reset (MR) | Header: [00 00 05] | Payload: [80]
    ESP->>W5500: Set Gateway (GAR) | Header: [00 01 07] | Payload: [0A 00 00 01]
    ESP->>W5500: Set Subnet Mask (SUBR) | Header: [00 05 07] | Payload: [FF FF FF 00]
    ESP->>W5500: Set Source IP (SIPR) | Header: [00 0F 07] | Payload: [0A 00 00 13]
    ESP->>W5500: Set Source MAC (SHAR) | Header: [00 09 04] | Payload: [00 08 DC 01 02 03]

    Note over ESP, W5500: 2. Interrupt Setup & RAM Allocation (4KB per Buffer)

    ESP->>W5500: Enable S0 Int in SIMR | Header: [00 18 05] | Payload: [01]
    ESP->>W5500: Set S0 RX Buffer to 4KB | Header: [00 1E 0D] | Payload: [04]
    ESP->>W5500: Set S0 TX Buffer to 4KB | Header: [00 1F 0D] | Payload: [04]
    ESP->>W5500: Enable all S0 sub-interrupts (Sn_IMR) | Header: [00 2C 0D] | Payload: [FF]

    Note over ESP, W5500: 3. Open UDP Protocol for Socket 0

    ESP->>W5500: Set Sn_MR to UDP Mode (0x02) | Header: [00 00 0D] | Payload: [02]
    ESP->>W5500: Set Local Port to 5000 (0x1388) | Header: [00 04 0E] | Payload: [13 88]
    ESP->>W5500: Execute OPEN Command | Header: [00 01 0D] | Payload: [01]
    
    W5500-->>ESP: Read Sn_SR (Expect SOCK_UDP: 0x22) | Header: [00 03 09] | Payload: [22]

    Note over ESP, W5500: UDP Communication Ready!

    loop Routine Check
        ESP->>W5500: Read VERSIONR (0x0039) | Header: [00 39 01] | Payload: [00]
        W5500-->>ESP: Confirm Hardware Version | Header: [00 39 01] | Payload: [04]
    end